Class ArrayUnorderedList<T>

java.lang.Object
tp_ed.structures.ArrayList<T>
tp_ed.structures.ArrayUnorderedList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements held in this list
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable, ListADT<T>, UnorderedListADT<T>
public class ArrayUnorderedList<T> extends ArrayList<T> implements UnorderedListADT<T>
The ArrayUnorderedList class represents an unordered list implemented using an array. It extends ArrayList and implements the UnorderedListADT interface, providing methods to add elements to the front, rear, or after a specific target element in the list.
